{"tid":2455101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雞排妹遭酸「愛露還怕性騷擾」，館長開轟：性感不代表隨便","createTime":"2021-03-20T19:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T06:30:38.000Z","uid":74339,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c702e058247a1e604c27a3da14d89de923a5aa","tid":2455101,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://borderlessnoticia.com/watch_cDY5cDdZQ0Y5NFpvakJSMEUyRmdlUT09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fborderlessnoticia.com%2Fwatch_cDY5cDdZQ0Y5NFpvakJSMEUyRmdlUT09&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=0a6213e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://borderlessnoticia.com/watch_cDY5cDdZQ0Y5NFpvakJSMEUyRmdlUT09</a><br />\n<br />\n「雞排妹比起演藝圈那些假道學,好太多了」<br />\n<br />\n「隨便也不代表可以被性騷擾」<br />\n<br />\n「一個是誘 一個是惑難免會發生意外」<br />\n<br />\n「好比看到有錢人 不代表你可以去搶他錢 人家有錢是一回事 犯了法又是另外一回事😎」<br />\n<br />\n「這時候就一堆人在攻擊穿著，怎外面旗子廣告看板，一堆也是露的誇張就是沒有人會說話」<br />\n<br />\n「愛露.. 不代表愛玩.. 」<br />\n<br />\n「有些畜牲禽獸就是會把自己鮮添廉恥的價值觀表現的那麼明顯！硬是把性騷擾及別人代言的商品牽扯再一起！<br />\n若我說，你的屌可能成為強姦的證據來定你的罪！也是ＯＫ的嗎？那你女兒或你老婆是女性所以有機會賣淫！也是正確的嗎！？<br />\n人一藍腦就殘吧！藍營到底有多少陳萬固呢！？」"},{"pid":"8a8eb1f45bfe390c95d3dc4b94db844126377b77","tid":2455101,"uid":265839,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"魯迅：支那人眼中，露膊頭 = 雜交"},{"pid":"026f3954f565ecd99c5ccaec1624fbb22b37b6d5","tid":2455101,"uid":26014,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:09:56.000Z","msg":"人一藍腦就殘吧，原來呢句台灣都啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 館長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a3f6b543caea03fc3fb64459f580c23d241f8d","tid":2455101,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:14:00.000Z","msg":"反觀香港人自稱黃屍自稱手足，群起批鬥作為同路人既miss pun, 可想而知台灣人更有質素獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a3f5e341c35be517affd71c51547e75cbc1b28","tid":2455101